&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Colombo?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-colombo" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-colombo" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Colombo, the vibrant capital of Sri Lanka, is a city that beautifully blends the old with the new. As you wander through its bustling streets, you&amp;rsquo;ll find a mosaic of cultures, with colonial architecture standing side by side with modern skyscrapers. This rich historical tapestry is woven with influences from the Portuguese, Dutch, and British, making it a fascinating destination for history buffs and casual travelers alike. The city serves as a perfect introduction to Sri Lanka&amp;rsquo;s diverse culture, offering visitors a taste of its traditions, art, and cuisine.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>